gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Knicks 105, Trail Blazers 93
gameRecap.excerpt: Jalen Brunson leads the Knicks with 45 points and four assists for a 105-93 win over the Trail Blazers. Deandre Ayton tallied 31 points and 14 rebounds for the Trail Blazers in the losing effort. The Knicks improve to 39-27 on the season, while the Trail Blazers fall to 19-47.
